column10:
     OVERALL 7.0
   { Graphics }
- Beautiful 
   { Gameplay }
- Good/ sniping feel really realistic and satisfied / but sneaking mechanic is bullshit, you can barely complete a mission without alert the whole army 
   { Audio } 
- Good/ the sound of the enemy skull being crushed is very satisfying
   { PC Requirements }
- fast 
   { Story } 
- mediocre i guess / side characters are not memorable / the only thing you do is stop the Nazi from being too strong 
  { Game Time } 
- Average 
  { Should you buy it ? }
- If it's on sale
  { Bugs }
- Minor bugs 
  { My thought } 
- The reason why i bought this game is because it was on sale and i could shoot Hitler in the ball
